WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
ظآزDuring the dark nightظآز

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
ظآزA guiding lightظآز

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
ظآزJust like youظآز

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
ظآزMakes life turn brightظآز

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
ظآزBreaking free from darknessظآز

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
ظآزYou gave me strengthظآز

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
ظآزRunning for truthظآز

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
ظآزI find my pathظآز

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
ظآزDrawing on the hopeظآز

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
ظآزThat you render meظآز

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
ظآزIn this long journeyظآز

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
ظآزI run on lightlyظآز

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:47.080 --> 01:49.670
What do you want to be when you grow up?

01:50.470 --> 01:51.830
I want to be a doctor.

01:54.030 --> 01:55.200
But it's not because of my dad.

01:56.479 --> 01:57.560
It's because

01:58.520 --> 01:59.880
I've found something I want to do.

02:02.560 --> 02:03.310
And you?

02:10.350 --> 02:11.840
I want to get into

02:12.000 --> 02:13.570
Jiangzhou University's
Finance Department

02:13.570 --> 02:14.480
my parents talked about.

02:14.960 --> 02:16.240
Once I'm in the university,

02:16.560 --> 02:17.920
I'll get a part-time job

02:18.480 --> 02:19.920
to ease the burden on my family.

02:21.200 --> 02:23.280
My mom has toiled for her whole life.

02:23.560 --> 02:25.110
I want her to be treated

02:25.110 --> 02:26.430
and to rest.

02:28.079 --> 02:29.550
Also, I want to move my family

02:29.550 --> 02:31.390
out of the house in Chaoyang Village.

02:33.160 --> 02:35.470
I'm getting a bigger, newer house

02:36.240 --> 02:37.750
that belongs to me,

02:37.960 --> 02:39.190
Yu,

02:39.390 --> 02:41.190
Dad, Mom,

02:41.600 --> 02:43.750
and Beiyu.

02:44.440 --> 02:45.600
Qiao Qingyu.

02:47.190 --> 02:48.670
You've got a lot ahead of you.

02:50.310 --> 02:51.670
I'll accomplish each of them.

02:53.240 --> 02:54.079
I have faith in you.

02:55.880 --> 02:56.910
You can do it.

03:05.540 --> 03:10.530
[Episode 22]
[A Lifetime of Remembering You]

03:17.390 --> 03:19.910
Hei, a friend of mine
asked for a 100,000 yuan loan.

03:19.910 --> 03:20.910
Has it been approved yet?

03:20.910 --> 03:22.440
He's been asking me.

03:23.520 --> 03:25.160
Can't you see I'm annoyed?

03:25.190 --> 03:26.390
Just drive the car.

03:27.030 --> 03:28.720
I don't have time for that.

03:30.390 --> 03:31.640
Punks.

03:32.079 --> 03:33.670
Punks.

03:35.670 --> 03:36.480
Who do you think you're abusing?

03:44.240 --> 03:45.480
Sun asked us

03:45.480 --> 03:47.990
to go over these workbooks.

03:48.270 --> 03:49.520
No need to pass it on to Sheng.

03:50.390 --> 03:52.670
He's preparing to go to Beining

03:52.670 --> 03:54.430
for the TEF.

03:55.079 --> 03:56.590
He's not coming back to school.

03:56.670 --> 03:58.800
We'll only get to meet him by chance.

03:59.079 --> 04:00.430
Sheng just left like that?

04:01.830 --> 04:03.080
He didn't even throw a farewell party.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.320
How heartless.

04:04.320 --> 04:05.150
Yeah.

04:05.150 --> 04:06.870
Buy a ticket and go find him.

04:06.920 --> 04:08.430
Perhaps you could catch a glimpse
of him leaving.

04:09.320 --> 04:10.800
He didn't use much of the workbook.

04:11.240 --> 04:12.800
I'll keep it for drafts.

04:12.800 --> 04:14.550
You're acting
like you're a model student.

04:14.920 --> 04:15.710
Deng Meixi.

04:17.709 --> 04:18.589
Such a moron.

04:41.360 --> 04:43.670
I heard something happened to Hei.

04:44.480 --> 04:45.920
He got beaten up and is hospitalized.

04:47.830 --> 04:49.760
We're not

04:49.870 --> 04:51.320
always unlucky.

04:51.990 --> 04:53.080
Also, your exam is coming up.

04:53.080 --> 04:54.390
Finally, my mind is at ease.

04:55.800 --> 04:57.870
We'll move once the exam is over.

05:28.080 --> 05:30.390
Mom, Dad's gone to the noodle house.

05:30.590 --> 05:32.110
He prepared something
and asked me to bring it home.

05:32.110 --> 05:33.270
Let's eat it while it's hot.

05:35.110 --> 05:36.320
Mom.

05:40.320 --> 05:41.470
Did you take all of them?

05:49.640 --> 05:50.640
Have some water.

05:55.710 --> 05:56.960
I took three pills,

05:58.830 --> 06:00.120
but I still couldn't sleep.

06:02.470 --> 06:03.470
Lie down for a bit.

06:29.230 --> 06:30.320
Are you feeling unwell?

06:33.560 --> 06:35.150
It's all my fault.

06:42.080 --> 06:43.080
No, it's not, Mom.

06:44.640 --> 06:46.150
Recently,

06:47.470 --> 06:48.790
I've been thinking

06:50.520 --> 06:52.960
why you were so strict with me.

06:56.150 --> 06:58.350
I realized I'm so lacking.

07:00.640 --> 07:02.080
I've kept so many things

07:03.270 --> 07:04.390
from you.

07:09.790 --> 07:10.590
Like

07:12.440 --> 07:13.790
the trip to Jiangzhou.

07:15.640 --> 07:18.390
I didn't go for the seminar.

07:23.470 --> 07:25.470
I went for a dance competition.

07:29.390 --> 07:31.440
I know you don't like me dancing.

07:33.350 --> 07:35.350
But when I dance,

07:35.350 --> 07:36.960
I feel so relaxed.

07:38.120 --> 07:38.909
Also...

07:43.390 --> 07:45.470
I wanted to fulfill Beiyu's wish.

07:49.790 --> 07:50.440
Mom.

07:53.320 --> 07:55.470
Are you disappointed in me?

07:59.520 --> 08:01.520
It's all my fault.

08:08.830 --> 08:10.790
I've grown up,

08:11.910 --> 08:13.880
and there's been so much more
weighing on my mind.

08:16.080 --> 08:18.350
But I kept them inside
and dared not tell you.

08:21.710 --> 08:23.590
But now I realize

08:24.150 --> 08:26.120
you're actually the one

08:26.120 --> 08:30.560
who loves me the most
and who are closest to me in this world.

08:34.440 --> 08:36.200
From now on, I'll tell you everything.

08:38.390 --> 08:39.200
All right?

08:44.470 --> 08:45.030
Hmm.

08:48.640 --> 08:51.440
When I transferred
to Huanzhou High School,

08:53.270 --> 08:54.910
I wasn't happy

08:57.120 --> 08:58.880
because of Beiyu,

09:01.030 --> 09:03.640
but I didn't tell you about that.

09:08.030 --> 09:10.000
There's only one person who helped me.

09:12.910 --> 09:14.030
That's Ming Sheng.

09:17.790 --> 09:19.390
Too young.

09:21.560 --> 09:22.150
What's it?

09:23.790 --> 09:25.200
Too young.

09:25.790 --> 09:26.960
I know, Mom.

09:26.960 --> 09:29.000
I've made it clear to him.

09:29.390 --> 09:31.200
Besides, he's going abroad.

09:32.350 --> 09:34.120
Nothing will happen between us.

09:43.640 --> 09:47.350
Mom, it's only over ten days
until the exam.

09:48.200 --> 09:49.520
But you know what?

09:50.560 --> 09:52.270
There's something

09:55.110 --> 09:57.560
I've been nervous about.

10:01.230 --> 10:02.040
I'm scared

10:04.080 --> 10:06.040
you will suddenly leave us

10:06.400 --> 10:08.200
as Beiyu did.

10:11.350 --> 10:12.990
I'm just tired.

10:16.560 --> 10:18.630
I'll be fine
after resting for a few days.

10:19.110 --> 10:21.590
Let's go rest at the hospital
for a while, all right?

10:23.470 --> 10:25.680
People will talk.

10:26.040 --> 10:28.800
Don't worry about what they say.

10:29.590 --> 10:32.200
Once the NCEE is over, I'll apply

10:32.200 --> 10:33.870
to the Finance Department
of Jiangzhou University as you said.

10:33.960 --> 10:35.960
I'll earn back all the money
for the medical bill.

10:36.630 --> 10:38.830
Promise me you'll go to the hospital
after the exam,

10:38.830 --> 10:39.560
all right?

10:41.990 --> 10:43.040
All right, Mom?

10:44.630 --> 10:45.440
Mom.

10:47.560 --> 10:48.230
Hmm.

11:10.880 --> 11:14.080
[Phenobarbital Tablets]

11:14.080 --> 11:23.480
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

11:25.030 --> 11:33.230
[To Let]

11:35.920 --> 11:36.440
Sure.

11:37.350 --> 11:39.230
It's good for girls to learn manicures.

11:39.680 --> 11:40.960
I don't really understand it,

11:41.350 --> 11:43.040
but it's definitely better
than working here.

11:43.680 --> 11:45.630
Pick up a new skill while you're young.

11:48.110 --> 11:48.990
Take this.

11:48.990 --> 11:49.920
I can't accept this.

11:50.590 --> 11:52.040
This is from me and your aunt.

11:52.960 --> 11:54.080
Thank you

11:55.160 --> 11:56.870
for looking after me

11:56.870 --> 11:57.830
during this time.

11:57.830 --> 12:00.920
You've helped us a lot.

12:00.920 --> 12:02.320
We should be the ones thanking you.

12:04.200 --> 12:05.750
Uncle, I'm leaving, then.

12:05.870 --> 12:08.040
Take care, Huan.

12:08.920 --> 12:09.960
Look after yourself.

12:10.110 --> 12:10.800
Hmm.

12:11.350 --> 12:11.990
I'm off.

12:11.990 --> 12:12.400
Come.

12:17.110 --> 12:18.280
Farewell, Uncle.

12:18.510 --> 12:19.040
Be careful.

12:19.040 --> 12:19.680
All right.

12:19.680 --> 12:20.510
See you, Huan.

12:20.510 --> 12:21.280
See you.

12:26.920 --> 12:27.990
Let's clean everything up.

12:29.040 --> 12:29.560
Oh, right.

12:29.560 --> 12:31.280
Go get the mop.

12:46.170 --> 12:55.920
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

13:05.230 --> 13:08.560
Sir, a bowl of noodles, please.

13:25.470 --> 13:26.560
Don't skip lunch.

13:28.160 --> 13:28.510
Bye.

13:43.710 --> 13:45.800
[Don't fail your youth]
Listen up, this is important.

13:47.280 --> 13:49.960
Let me stress again.

13:50.230 --> 13:51.470
Don't try questions

13:51.470 --> 13:53.320
that are too difficult for you.

13:53.630 --> 13:55.160
Focus on the basics.

13:56.160 --> 13:57.110
Remember what I told you?

13:57.110 --> 13:57.830
No matter how tricky the questions are,

13:57.830 --> 13:59.080
they won't go beyond our syllabus.

13:59.350 --> 14:00.230
Take this question as an example.

14:00.230 --> 14:01.960
Didn't we discuss it before?

14:03.340 --> 14:04.110
It says...

14:04.110 --> 14:06.560
[Seize every second to review
and work hard for good grades.]

14:06.560 --> 14:08.380
[Decade of dedication.
Three days to decide.]

14:08.730 --> 14:12.770
ظآزYou said something
I couldn't understandظآز

14:14.550 --> 14:18.030
ظآزAnd I realized my desireظآز

14:18.030 --> 14:20.690
[Huanzhou High School Grade 2, Class 5]
[Monthly Test Results, Sciences]

14:20.690 --> 14:21.760
[Qiao Qingyu, 10th]

14:21.760 --> 14:24.280
ظآزYou lit up a lampظآز

14:27.260 --> 14:30.840
ظآزI saw the lightظآز

14:31.110 --> 14:32.230
Get ready, everyone.

14:32.350 --> 14:33.870
Show a happy face. You're graduating.

14:33.870 --> 14:35.440
ظآزYou slowly walked awayظآز

14:35.440 --> 14:36.590
Please move closer.

14:38.590 --> 14:40.110
Teachers, relax.

14:40.830 --> 14:43.320
Good. Everyone, look at the camera.

14:43.710 --> 14:45.200
Say cheese.

14:46.320 --> 14:48.920
- We graduated!
- We graduated!

14:50.880 --> 14:54.860
ظآزIt's just a pretense of silenceظآز

14:57.230 --> 15:00.240
ظآزHow should I find comfortظآز

15:00.610 --> 15:02.310
ظآزIn the unknown years ahead?ظآز

15:03.100 --> 15:05.400
ظآزDon't be so miserable anymoreظآز

15:05.400 --> 15:07.110
Mumu, I hope this letter finds you well.

15:08.320 --> 15:09.160
In the blink of an eye,

15:09.200 --> 15:11.160
my NCEE is coming soon.

15:12.280 --> 15:14.160
While you've been studying in Beining
this past year,

15:14.590 --> 15:17.080
a lot has happened in Huanzhou.

15:18.150 --> 15:20.280
Thankfully, all the incidents
were resolved

15:20.710 --> 15:22.920
just in time for the exam.

15:23.830 --> 15:26.110
Nothing went off track.

15:28.830 --> 15:31.280
I think I've finally found the peace
I never had before.

15:32.200 --> 15:34.320
The confusion, loss,

15:34.990 --> 15:37.230
anger, and resentment are gone.

15:37.230 --> 15:39.230
ظآزWhy not run away and break free?ظآز

15:39.860 --> 15:44.460
ظآزThere's no other way for meظآز

15:45.160 --> 15:46.280
In this peace,

15:46.710 --> 15:48.710
I feel a strong strength in me

15:48.800 --> 15:51.600
[All wishes come true]
to lead my family to a better future.

15:52.590 --> 15:55.470
For the first time, I can see clearly

15:55.590 --> 15:57.230
my path ahead.

15:58.200 --> 15:59.960
NCEE, moving to a new place,

16:00.510 --> 16:01.920
studying finance in Jiangzhou,

16:02.710 --> 16:04.280
and finding a job four years later.

16:04.990 --> 16:08.040
I'll take each and every step firmly
to give my family a better life.

16:15.080 --> 16:17.240
[NCEE is a starting point, not the end.
Make sure you have no regrets.]

16:33.120 --> 16:39.080
ظآزYou never know. Maybe todayظآز

16:39.610 --> 16:44.940
ظآزThere is a breakthrough coming.
There is a turning pointظآز

16:44.940 --> 16:50.430
ظآز'Cause something changed.
I feel it in the atmosphereظآز

16:50.430 --> 16:56.230
ظآزThere's a dawning of a new dayظآز

16:58.550 --> 17:03.780
ظآزI see the end inside.
I don't know if I can carry it onظآز

17:03.780 --> 17:09.210
ظآزWill the burden break me?ظآز

17:10.030 --> 17:15.390
ظآزI reach for the other side
as the world begins to shakeظآز

17:15.859 --> 17:18.260
ظآزI come back to lifeظآز

17:19.770 --> 17:27.310
ظآزNow I feel just like I can flyظآز

17:28.099 --> 17:30.930
ظآزNot coming downظآز

17:31.460 --> 17:42.930
ظآزI feel just like I can fly.
Can't bring me downظآز

17:49.870 --> 17:50.470
Qingyu!

17:53.590 --> 17:54.400
This is strange.

17:55.110 --> 17:58.280
Youth before the exam
feels long, heavy, and intense,

17:59.200 --> 18:01.680
yet it barely registers

18:01.680 --> 18:02.750
in the grand scheme of life.

18:04.040 --> 18:05.280
That doesn't seem fair.

18:06.350 --> 18:10.080
I guess life must be very long.

18:11.400 --> 18:13.320
[Everything Goes Well]
"Life goes on and on."

18:13.830 --> 18:16.510
I think that means

18:17.590 --> 18:19.440
life continues,

18:20.080 --> 18:22.230
whether it goes as planned or not.

18:22.830 --> 18:24.630
Eventually, it becomes the past.

18:25.590 --> 18:28.600
The future is what truly matters.

18:28.600 --> 18:32.920
ظآزI feel just like I can flyظآز

18:32.920 --> 18:34.960
What a spread. I must have a drink.

18:34.960 --> 18:37.640
Try Qingyu and my cooking.

18:37.750 --> 18:39.120
Your cooking?

18:39.120 --> 18:40.120
I prepared all this.

18:40.120 --> 18:41.960
How is this not my cooking?

18:42.160 --> 18:43.990
Didn't I prepare the green beans?

18:43.990 --> 18:45.470
Didn't I rinse the rice?

18:46.510 --> 18:47.310
Try them.

18:47.310 --> 18:47.990
Let me take a bite.

18:48.120 --> 18:51.070
This is my first time eating a meal
I didn't have to cook.

18:54.400 --> 18:55.160
How does it taste?

18:55.160 --> 18:56.550
Not bad.

18:56.680 --> 18:57.990
I'll give it a try.

18:58.440 --> 18:59.440
In that case, I'll cook every day
from now on.

19:03.880 --> 19:06.990
What's this? Tomato and rubber stew?

19:07.270 --> 19:08.200
Dad, Mom,

19:08.200 --> 19:09.400
you should

19:09.400 --> 19:10.470
take the kitchen back.

19:10.680 --> 19:11.270
Don't listen to him.

19:11.270 --> 19:13.360
I'll practice more over these two months
during the summer vacation.

19:13.550 --> 19:14.550
Dad, can you give me some advice?

19:14.550 --> 19:17.120
Are you sure you only need two months?

19:17.120 --> 19:18.360
Oh, come on.

19:18.400 --> 19:19.120
Shut up and eat.

19:19.400 --> 19:20.310
Pretty good.

19:20.310 --> 19:22.270
Chew a few more times.

19:22.920 --> 19:24.360
Look, Dad says it's delicious.

19:24.440 --> 19:25.230
Delicious.

19:25.510 --> 19:27.510
This is Qingyu's first time cooking.

19:27.510 --> 19:28.440
I think she's done pretty well.

19:28.440 --> 19:30.200
We didn't have to do anything
and now we're eating.

19:30.440 --> 19:31.920
Anyway, we're happy.

19:33.400 --> 19:34.440
Here. Thank you, Qingyu.

19:35.310 --> 19:35.840
Come on.

19:35.840 --> 19:36.990
Cheers.

19:39.920 --> 19:40.550
Eat up.

19:41.270 --> 19:42.640
The drink tastes better.

19:47.700 --> 19:53.960
ظآزIt's like with a matter I never know.
Gonna start againظآز

19:54.270 --> 19:57.870
ظآزTake it up and start again
'cause it's changingظآز

19:57.870 --> 19:59.740
[Admission Notice]

20:03.070 --> 20:03.640
Qiao.

20:03.640 --> 20:04.360
It has arrived!

20:05.070 --> 20:05.790
Look at this.

20:05.790 --> 20:07.310
She made it!

20:08.070 --> 20:09.360
Look how happy he is.

20:09.360 --> 20:12.850
ظآزWe are changingظآز

20:17.960 --> 20:19.560
ظآزCome on nowظآز

20:20.650 --> 20:24.760
ظآزAnd I feel just like I can flyظآز

20:24.760 --> 20:28.550
[Jiangzhou University Admission Notice]

20:28.680 --> 20:31.580
ظآزNot coming downظآز

20:32.130 --> 20:43.150
ظآزI feel just like I can fly.
Can't bring me downظآز

20:46.150 --> 20:54.400
ظآزNow I feel just like I can fly.
Can't bring me downظآز

21:08.440 --> 21:09.710
It's chilly.

21:09.960 --> 21:10.640
Yes.

21:13.640 --> 21:15.550
It's been a long while
since I went to a shopping mall.

21:16.070 --> 21:19.030
Things are so different now.

21:19.310 --> 21:20.550
This is a new mall.

21:20.550 --> 21:21.920
What are all these?

21:22.750 --> 21:25.310
These are skincare products
and cosmetics.

21:30.920 --> 21:33.470
Young people these days
have so many choices.

21:40.470 --> 21:41.070
Do you want it?

21:42.070 --> 21:42.880
No need, Mom.

21:42.880 --> 21:43.600
Let's go.

21:43.790 --> 21:46.070
The function of these two are the same.

21:46.070 --> 21:47.960
They're for hydration.

21:48.200 --> 21:49.030
Please take a look at this.

21:49.600 --> 21:50.920
Please take a look.

21:51.400 --> 21:52.680
Hi.

21:52.680 --> 21:53.880
Would you like to pick some lipsticks?

21:53.880 --> 21:54.790
Feel free to take a look.

21:58.360 --> 21:59.310
Try it.

22:08.440 --> 22:09.440
Nice.

22:10.120 --> 22:10.790
Pretty.

22:12.710 --> 22:14.750
My daughter is pretty.

22:15.160 --> 22:18.200
Mom, isn't this shade too red?

22:18.310 --> 22:19.030
No.

22:19.030 --> 22:21.470
This shade complements
your skin tone beautifully.

22:21.600 --> 22:23.750
It makes you look elegant.

22:23.750 --> 22:24.440
Have a look.

22:24.990 --> 22:25.790
We'll take this.

22:25.790 --> 22:26.360
Sure.

22:28.030 --> 22:28.960
Wait.

22:31.750 --> 22:32.640
And this too.

22:32.640 --> 22:33.710
All right. One moment.

22:44.160 --> 22:44.960
Well.

22:46.920 --> 22:48.270
Lipsticks only look good

22:48.270 --> 22:50.310
on young girls.

22:50.880 --> 22:53.550
I'm too old for it.

22:53.960 --> 22:55.640
I want you to look pretty too.

22:55.840 --> 22:57.750
Look at those photos
when you were young.

22:57.880 --> 22:59.550
That blue eye shadow and red lipstick.

22:59.600 --> 23:01.550
Those eyelashes are so curly.

23:01.550 --> 23:02.270
You were so stylish back then.

23:02.270 --> 23:04.640
That was over twenty years ago.

23:05.120 --> 23:05.640
Mom,

23:06.070 --> 23:08.030
don't just focus

23:08.030 --> 23:09.600
on me and Yu.

23:09.750 --> 23:12.030
You should put more focus on yourself.

23:16.230 --> 23:18.270
I was too strict with you back then.

23:19.990 --> 23:22.470
When you're at your new school, be happy

23:22.470 --> 23:23.600
and make more friends.

23:27.270 --> 23:28.230
You've grown up.

23:57.360 --> 24:00.790
ظآزUnder the sunlightظآز

24:00.790 --> 24:04.610
ظآزBirds take a flyظآز

24:04.610 --> 24:09.240
ظآزRaise me up, hold me highظآز

24:09.240 --> 24:12.540
ظآزOnly youظآز

24:13.110 --> 24:17.590
ظآزDuring the dark nightظآز

24:17.590 --> 24:21.060
ظآزA guiding lightظآز

24:21.060 --> 24:22.690
ظآزJust like youظآز

24:22.690 --> 24:27.640
ظآزMakes life turn brightظآز

24:27.640 --> 24:32.750
ظآزBreaking free from darknessظآز

24:32.750 --> 24:37.550
ظآزYou gave me strengthظآز

24:37.550 --> 24:39.990
ظآزRunning for truthظآز

24:39.990 --> 24:45.040
ظآزI find my pathظآز

24:45.040 --> 24:49.260
ظآزDrawing on the hopeظآز

24:49.260 --> 24:52.860
ظآزThat you render meظآز

24:52.860 --> 24:56.210
ظآزIn this long journeyظآز

24:56.210 --> 24:58.830
ظآزI run lightlyظآز

25:28.120 --> 25:29.360
Let's have a toast.

25:29.640 --> 25:31.230
Happy graduation.

25:31.400 --> 25:32.470
Finally, we're free.

25:36.120 --> 25:38.360
Everything feels lighter
after getting the admission notice.

25:38.640 --> 25:40.360
The swim was fantastic.

25:40.640 --> 25:41.600
It was awesome.

25:42.120 --> 25:44.360
Everyone here
will have different professions.

25:44.790 --> 25:47.070
The future national athlete.

25:48.710 --> 25:49.600
Diplomat.

25:50.030 --> 25:50.840
Diplomat.

25:50.960 --> 25:51.880
Dentist.

25:51.880 --> 25:52.200
Hmm.

25:52.200 --> 25:53.710
The future financial analyst.

25:53.710 --> 25:54.400
Dentist.

25:54.400 --> 25:57.030
And the owner
of an international enterprise.

25:57.470 --> 25:59.550
Doing international trading
with that low math grade?

25:59.550 --> 26:01.310
A diplomat with poor English?

26:01.310 --> 26:02.160
Stop mocking me.

26:02.550 --> 26:03.990
Anyway,

26:03.990 --> 26:06.400
she didn't mention
the most impressive one.

26:06.750 --> 26:08.600
Acting Department of Chuanxi University.

26:08.600 --> 26:09.270
A round of applause.

26:10.470 --> 26:11.790
The future superstar.

26:11.790 --> 26:13.120
Superstar.

26:13.270 --> 26:14.710
Don't forget us when you're famous.

26:14.710 --> 26:15.470
That's possible.

26:15.510 --> 26:16.790
If you forget us,

26:16.790 --> 26:18.880
we'll post your embarrassing photos
during high school.

26:18.880 --> 26:19.510
You're not doing that!

26:19.960 --> 26:22.230
I remember you always sleeping in class

26:22.230 --> 26:23.400
and drooling.

26:23.400 --> 26:26.270
Has Ming Sheng left for France yet?

26:30.920 --> 26:32.030
He...

26:33.880 --> 26:35.470
I don't have time for that.

26:35.840 --> 26:37.550
So clueless.

26:37.880 --> 26:38.680
Punks.

26:39.710 --> 26:41.310
Punks.

26:44.710 --> 26:45.550
Who do you think you're talking to?

26:45.550 --> 26:47.270
You, punks.

26:48.230 --> 26:50.790
Brat.

26:53.960 --> 26:55.120
Say that again.

26:55.120 --> 26:56.160
Are you deaf?

26:56.680 --> 26:57.470
Punks.

26:58.600 --> 26:59.400
Get him!

27:00.790 --> 27:01.750
Who are you calling punks, huh?

27:02.360 --> 27:03.920
Shut him up! Give him a good slap!

27:05.400 --> 27:07.230
Knock some sense into him!

27:08.790 --> 27:09.920
Brat.

27:11.440 --> 27:12.230
Beat him up.

27:21.440 --> 27:22.790
Chase him. Beat him up!

27:23.070 --> 27:24.160
He deserves a good beating!

27:43.310 --> 27:44.400
Brat.

27:51.600 --> 27:52.230
You little brat.

27:52.230 --> 27:53.510
Say that again.

27:53.680 --> 27:55.400
Say that again if you can.

27:55.400 --> 27:55.710
Come on.

27:55.710 --> 27:57.200
Do it, brat.

27:57.200 --> 27:57.710
Do it!

28:14.710 --> 28:16.750
Sheng fought alone
against the three of them.

28:17.120 --> 28:17.920
In the end,

28:17.960 --> 28:19.960
he broke Hei's rib.

28:21.510 --> 28:22.600
Hei was arrested.

28:22.880 --> 28:24.070
Sheng was also seriously injured.

28:24.840 --> 28:26.120
He couldn't stand seeing your family

28:27.550 --> 28:29.750
living in fear,

28:30.400 --> 28:31.920
so he took care of Hei

28:31.920 --> 28:34.120
before heading to France.

28:36.230 --> 28:37.160
Fortunately,

28:37.880 --> 28:39.200
Hei and his gang started the fight,

28:39.750 --> 28:41.400
so Sheng was considered
to be in self-defense.

28:45.070 --> 28:46.070
When did you come back?

28:47.600 --> 28:48.990
I thought you were abroad.

28:49.920 --> 28:51.440
Didn't I say so?

28:52.790 --> 28:54.600
I'll always stand by you.

28:55.510 --> 28:57.270
You're more eager to leave home
than I am.

28:58.200 --> 29:00.070
This is only a game to you.

29:00.120 --> 29:00.920
You're right.

29:00.920 --> 29:02.920
ظآزCounting the distance that separates usظآز

29:02.920 --> 29:04.510
I'm willing to risk my future

29:05.710 --> 29:06.990
and everything for this game.

29:07.790 --> 29:08.600
Ming Sheng.

29:09.470 --> 29:10.270
I wonder

29:11.200 --> 29:12.710
as we grow older

29:13.270 --> 29:15.600
and our lives fill with new experiences

29:16.270 --> 29:17.990
and people,

29:18.880 --> 29:19.920
will

29:21.920 --> 29:23.680
our memories of this time

29:25.440 --> 29:27.160
eventually fade?

29:27.160 --> 29:30.640
ظآزPerhapsظآز

29:31.320 --> 29:36.870
ظآزWe were afraid of losingظآز

29:36.920 --> 29:37.470
Don't be afraid.

29:39.070 --> 29:39.790
I'm here with you.

29:39.790 --> 29:43.520
ظآزThat's why we were hesitantظآز

29:44.070 --> 29:44.710
Do you remember

29:44.710 --> 29:46.030
the first time we met?

29:47.310 --> 29:48.550
You bit me.

29:50.440 --> 29:51.710
Today, I bit you back.

29:52.200 --> 29:53.640
Now we're even.

29:53.640 --> 29:57.700
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

29:58.550 --> 30:02.230
ظآزIs your nameظآز

30:02.700 --> 30:07.930
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

30:08.630 --> 30:10.840
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

30:10.840 --> 30:12.230
I noticed it

30:12.230 --> 30:13.550
when I first moved here.

30:14.470 --> 30:16.070
To be fair,

30:17.200 --> 30:18.880
I met it

30:18.990 --> 30:20.200
before you.

30:20.200 --> 30:22.650
ظآزOnly then does time
not betray our acquaintanceظآز

30:26.510 --> 30:28.920
No take-backs.

30:40.030 --> 30:41.510
From now on, I'll erase

30:41.750 --> 30:43.510
ظآزFutureظآز

30:43.510 --> 30:44.790
all the memories about you.

30:46.330 --> 30:49.070
ظآزTime will reveal this secretظآز

30:49.070 --> 30:50.440
I wish you the best of luck.

30:53.610 --> 30:59.000
ظآزWaiting is a silent promiseظآز

30:59.890 --> 31:01.640
ظآزThat never expiresظآز

31:01.640 --> 31:02.550
I didn't know

31:02.550 --> 31:04.510
you've done so much for me.

31:08.600 --> 31:11.160
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

31:11.160 --> 31:12.750
Since you broke the promise,

31:14.330 --> 31:17.400
ظآزIs your nameظآز

31:17.400 --> 31:18.960
I'll also take back my words.

31:18.960 --> 31:22.160
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

31:22.160 --> 31:23.840
I will remember you forever.

31:24.640 --> 31:25.400
Qiao Qingyu.

31:25.400 --> 31:26.920
ظآزAt first sightظآز

31:26.920 --> 31:28.360
I'm so glad we met.

31:28.360 --> 31:31.320
ظآزThe future has been determinedظآز

31:32.030 --> 31:33.360
Me too!

31:34.310 --> 31:36.790
All the best to us.

31:37.880 --> 31:38.990
All the best.

31:38.990 --> 31:41.970
ظآزTurns out that what's on your mindظآز

31:42.450 --> 31:46.480
ظآزIs a placeظآز

31:46.910 --> 31:52.200
ظآزWhere the same story is held dearظآز

31:52.950 --> 31:56.230
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

31:56.770 --> 31:59.960
ظآزCourage wasn't late tooظآز

32:00.540 --> 32:06.670
ظآزOnly then does time
not betray our acquaintanceظآز

32:25.680 --> 32:26.310
Dad.

32:26.360 --> 32:26.920
Hmm?

32:27.270 --> 32:28.600
I didn't tell you

32:28.600 --> 32:30.360
that I went to Jiangzhou
for the dance competition.

32:30.710 --> 32:32.160
Why would you help me?

32:35.960 --> 32:37.070
I know you well.

32:41.470 --> 32:42.840
I was young once.

33:03.320 --> 33:07.050
[Tomb of Our Beloved Daughter
Qiao Beiyu]

33:13.790 --> 33:16.030
Beiyu, we're here to visit you.

34:02.990 --> 34:03.990
Beiyu.

34:05.510 --> 34:07.120
We're here to visit you.

34:07.400 --> 34:09.550
Many things have happened recently.

34:11.400 --> 34:12.550
I was afraid I might forget,

34:13.159 --> 34:14.679
so I wrote it down.

34:15.400 --> 34:17.199
Let me read it for you.

34:20.469 --> 34:24.199
Bei, things are getting better.

34:24.880 --> 34:26.120
Qing did a great job.

34:26.120 --> 34:28.710
She got into the Finance Department
at Jiangzhou University.

34:29.510 --> 34:30.920
She even arranged

34:30.920 --> 34:32.510
for my hospital stay.

34:34.120 --> 34:36.070
I'll be going there
the day after tomorrow.

34:36.880 --> 34:39.880
Jinyu is also doing pretty well
in his studies.

34:40.159 --> 34:41.600
He's been working hard.

34:41.989 --> 34:47.230
The teacher believes
he can earn an associate's degree.

34:47.920 --> 34:50.510
The house back in Shunyun has been sold,

34:50.790 --> 34:53.400
and all the debt has been cleared.

34:54.070 --> 34:55.310
Your dad used the rest of the money

34:55.710 --> 34:58.310
to buy a small house in Xingzhou.

34:59.070 --> 35:02.230
It's not a big place,
but it's in a really nice spot.

35:03.360 --> 35:05.920
His tenosynovitis
has been acting up again.

35:06.120 --> 35:07.400
It's quite serious,

35:08.360 --> 35:09.790
so he can't cook

35:10.310 --> 35:11.960
for the time being.

35:12.440 --> 35:13.990
We've talked about it.

35:14.440 --> 35:16.470
Since the noodle house doesn't work out,

35:17.400 --> 35:20.120
we'll find other less demanding jobs

35:20.400 --> 35:22.360
in Xingzhou.

35:23.270 --> 35:24.710
After Qingyu graduated,

35:25.400 --> 35:27.310
our pressure has been much eased.

35:28.230 --> 35:31.800
We're doing okay.
You must be doing well, right?

35:38.280 --> 35:41.550
Beiyu, once Mom is discharged,

35:42.110 --> 35:43.920
we'll start anew.

35:44.550 --> 35:46.440
Don't worry, all right?

35:49.760 --> 35:50.720
I believe

35:51.440 --> 35:53.400
everything can start over.

35:54.320 --> 35:55.150
[Tomb of Our Beloved Daughter]
Beiyu.

35:55.920 --> 35:57.470
[Qiao Beiyu]
If I get a chance,

35:57.470 --> 35:59.320
I'll go back to Nanqiao Village

35:59.630 --> 36:01.470
to visit the place where you grew up.

36:22.670 --> 36:24.920
This is where I found your sister.

36:30.070 --> 36:33.960
If I hadn't found her

36:34.920 --> 36:36.190
and run after her,

36:36.190 --> 36:37.070
what would've happened to her?

36:38.150 --> 36:39.920
What do you think
she was thinking at that time?

36:40.760 --> 36:41.550
Mom,

36:42.630 --> 36:44.070
Beiyu has passed for quite some time.

36:45.070 --> 36:46.320
That's all behind us now.

36:53.880 --> 36:55.320
Let's sit here for a bit.

37:02.110 --> 37:03.920
She was like a bird,

37:05.440 --> 37:07.110
standing still

37:08.720 --> 37:11.110
and looking up at the sky.

37:17.030 --> 37:19.320
How she wished to know
what it felt like to fly.

37:20.510 --> 37:22.960
She had no idea
how high she could reach.

37:24.470 --> 37:27.190
She wondered why the ocean

37:27.190 --> 37:29.280
was as blue as the sky.

37:30.880 --> 37:33.550
Would she stay with her parents forever

37:33.550 --> 37:34.990
at the edge of the sky?

37:37.840 --> 37:38.840
It was cold.

37:39.920 --> 37:41.070
She was scared.

37:42.400 --> 37:44.800
Below her, there was an abyss.

37:45.110 --> 37:47.400
She didn't know
if she could fly across it.

37:51.190 --> 37:53.630
Finally, she spread her wings.

38:12.630 --> 38:13.440
Let me.

38:26.150 --> 38:26.960
Mom,

38:27.550 --> 38:29.960
this box is for your use
in the hospital.

38:30.320 --> 38:32.480
And I'm taking this to Jiangzhou.

38:32.960 --> 38:34.880
And this one is for Yu.

38:35.280 --> 38:37.030
The rest will be moved to the new place.

38:37.110 --> 38:38.440
I've arranged a car.

38:38.470 --> 38:40.070
It's the corner shop's van.

38:40.360 --> 38:42.110
Madam Yang said we're neighbors,

38:42.110 --> 38:43.320
so she won't charge us a fee.

38:45.760 --> 38:46.550
Don't worry.

38:46.880 --> 38:49.190
I'll make sure to bring
all the important things.

38:52.670 --> 38:53.550
Sweet dreams.

38:56.630 --> 38:58.110
You too, Mom.

40:28.030 --> 40:28.800
Beiyu.

40:32.990 --> 40:35.720
Qiao Beiyu!

40:37.960 --> 40:38.760
Qing.

40:40.880 --> 40:42.960
I can't continue this journey with you.

40:44.670 --> 40:46.470
The views ahead are beautiful.

40:46.840 --> 40:48.320
Enjoy them for me.

40:52.760 --> 40:53.590
Don't worry.

40:55.360 --> 40:57.280
I'll take good care of our family,

40:58.590 --> 41:00.280
for your sake.

41:32.280 --> 41:35.970
ظآزPerhapsظآز

41:36.480 --> 41:42.180
ظآزThe more we care,
the more careful we becomeظآز

41:43.320 --> 41:48.720
ظآزCounting the distance
that separates usظآز

41:49.720 --> 41:55.280
ظآزA single step,
and we'd be closer stillظآز

42:00.950 --> 42:04.620
ظآزIn the futureظآز

42:05.080 --> 42:10.800
ظآزTime will reveal this secretظآز

42:12.300 --> 42:17.370
ظآزWaiting is a silent promiseظآز

42:18.620 --> 42:23.780
ظآزThat never expiresظآز

42:27.380 --> 42:31.850
ظآزTurns out that what's on my mindظآز

42:32.850 --> 42:36.520
ظآزIs your nameظآز

42:37.020 --> 42:42.120
ظآزThe only stubbornness in my heartظآز

42:43.200 --> 42:46.420
ظآزAt first sightظآز

42:46.850 --> 42:50.130
ظآزThe future has been determinedظآز

42:50.820 --> 42:56.380
ظآزDreams began to feel realظآز

42:57.480 --> 43:01.020
ظآزTurns out that what's on your mindظآز

43:01.480 --> 43:05.420
ظآزIs a placeظآز

43:05.720 --> 43:11.280
ظآزWhere the same story is held dearظآز

43:11.950 --> 43:15.320
ظآزFortunately, I'm not sensible enoughظآز

43:15.650 --> 43:19.120
ظآزCourage wasn't late tooظآز

43:19.650 --> 43:25.720
ظآزOnly then does time not betray
our acquaintanceظآز
